  "text": "The reaction mixture contained the following components in a total volume of 12. . Incubation was carried out at room temperature for 30 min, and the reaction products were separated on 4% non-denaturing polyacrylamide gels, which were subsequently dried and autoradiographed. The binding specificities of the probes were evaluated by incubating the extracts with an excess of nonlabeled wild type and mutant EBS oligonucleotides [CITATION_1] .",
